1 Day Ago Rohr came under heavy criticism after he called up Ahmed Musa for last month’s AFCON qualifiers against Benin and Lesotho. He won his 96th cap with the Eagles as a late substitute against Lesotho. The second round of the 2022 World Cup qualifiers begin in June, with Nigeria drawn in the same group as Cape Verde, Central African Republic and Liberia.